modules.description: Provides functions to select and retrieve images from a device's gallery, with support for resizing and quality adjustment. Operates on image data structures including file paths, base64 encoded strings, and binary buffers. Used to implement photo upload features in mobile applications requiring user-selected media.

Provides functions to configure image selection parameters and retrieve selected images from the device. Operates with an opaque options type and string arrays representing image paths. Used to capture and process multiple images with specified resolution and quality constraints.
